data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCaseAssignment
data.value: select EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE where @casNo = CAS_NO order by DISCONTINUE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, MODIFICATIONS from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = 'JD'

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, MODIFICATIONS from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadInfrastructureCase
data.value: select * from ( select SYSTEM_GENERATED_I, EVENT_ID, REASON_CODE, CASE_NUMBER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, REFERENCE_DATE from CKT_INFRASTRUCTURE where EVENT_ID = 8 and CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp and REASON_CODE = 'MODFNRVWDT' and (REFERENCE_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) NUMB, STATUS, STATUS_DATE, NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE where ( STATUS = 'C' and (STATUS_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) or STATUS = 'O' ) and NO_JURISDICTION_CD <= ' ' and NUMB = S1.CASE_NUMBER ) S2 order by S1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority35
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, MODIFICATIONS = @modifications where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
